      "y": 110,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 480,
      "text": "📊\nData\nOnboarding\nAgent\n\nRun: Per source\n\nPhases:\n0. Health Check\n1. Discovery\n2. Validation\n3. Profiling\n4. Artifacts\n   (spawns 4\n    sub-agents)\n5. Deployment\n\nCreates:\n• Bronze→\n  Silver→Gold\n• Glue jobs\n• Airflow DAG\n• Quality checks\n• LF-Tags",
